{"about_the_game":"After accidentally joining a cult, and quickly realizing their mistake, one cultist resolves to find a way out before they-to become another one of the countless victims of The Stronghold.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480910/extras/solve_puzzles.png?t=1654865483\" /><br><br>There are a lot of locked doors between you and the nearest exit. Fortunately, most of them can be opened with good old-fashioned brain power.<br>Push blocks, manipulate sentrymen, redirect boulders, and do whatever else may be necessary to keep moving forward.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480910/extras/dodge_deadly_traps.png?t=1654865483\" /><br><br>The Stronghold isn't a safe place. With dart traps, loads of sawblades, and more spikes than any building should reasonably have, it's nothing short of a miracle that there are any cultists left.<br>Pay close attention to your surroundings to spot these traps, and you may make it out fully intact.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480910/extras/Face_the_higher_ups.png?t=1654865483\" /><br><br>Some doors can't be opened with critical thinking alone. These ones require special keys held by the Higher-Ups. While it may seem straight-forward, getting these keys will be no easy task; But, it's the only way you'll have any chance of making it out of here alive.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480910/extras/find_a_way_out.png?t=1654865483\" /><br><br>With nothing but your wits and your trusty dagger, can you survive long enough to find a way out? <br>Or will you be The Stronghold's next victim?","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Home Sweet Home","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1480910/207c24a15d9c15f264515